		"countryDescription": "<a href=\"https://www.dariah.ch\">Visit the DARIAH-CH website</a>.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"\">DARIAH-CH coordinates and promotes Swiss activities in the Digital Research Infrastructure for the Arts and Humanities (DARIAH). It is located at the Data and Service Center for the Humanities (DaSCH), the national infrastructure that </span><span class=\"\">operates a platform for humanities research data that ensures long-term access. Furthermore, the linking of data with other databases is promoted (linked open data), in order to create added value for further research and the interested public.</span>",
